{
  "stem": "19441.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 533.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she said, I see there a brother who is very far away, in danger.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he is even more afraid of your future.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So next day she said, imagine, she knew that I have a brother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and he's worrying about me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Why you think he's worrying about me?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Do you think he's worrying because the war is going to end and I have a bad reputation?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That I am beating the people with the whip?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said, who knows?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It could be.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So what do you think?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I shouldn't beat the people?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You like your brother?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He's the only thing that I have in life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, that if you want to please him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, by what will happen?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't beat the people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can do any other things but that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From that moment, she didn't beat them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That's what you had to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So on the day of March-- we'll go back to the death marching.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hmm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The death march.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now it-- it was, again, that the Russian are coming close.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they marched us again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From-- no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Malchow, further on, inside Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I didn't march too long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because a Russian woman who, once in a while, they had been in my barrack.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they was Partisans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They looked for me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they found me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they looked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Magda, Magda, Magda.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, Magda, we came to pick you up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the Russians are very close.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In a day or two, they will be here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But if somebody points a finger of you, they not only will rape you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they will beat-- tear you in pieces.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because you, they consider you a German helper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they are very bad with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they consider that I help the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
